{"tid":2135370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"托住樓價的「還息不還本」計劃將於10月31日終止","createTime":"2020-08-01T11:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T11:31:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58bf75a3c48c04c70998a1e4efa3dceadd411f2a","tid":2135370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"香港業主失業也不用急於賣樓套現, 原因之一是金管局的「還息不還本」計劃<br />\n<br />\n業主只需要還住低息先<br />\n<br />\n失業, 生意倒閉, 也不是即時要套現, 可以頂住先<br />\n<br />\n可惜, 呢樣嘢會於10月31日終止<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/04/20200417-3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fnews-and-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F04%2F20200417-3%2F&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=34b1b3c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/04/20200417-3/</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年04月17日<br />\n銀行業推出企業客戶「預先批核還息不還本」計劃<br />\n<br />\n金管局今日聯同「銀行業中小企貸款協調機制」宣布推出「預先批核還息不還本」安排予合資格企業客戶，計劃重點如下﹕<br />\n合資格客戶於<strong><span class=\"red\">2020年5月1日至10月31日6個月期間的所有貸款本金還款獲自動延期</span></strong>，一般貸款（包括循環貸款）的本金還款延期6個月，貿易融資貸款因應其短期性質，本金還款延期3個月"},{"pid":"61b87c01f88ed0631dab4ea3aeec3938fb623724","tid":2135370,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57f97f53dc9cf5a1a4d8f9b4204d41ee353225f","tid":2135370,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"永續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed5335775421387d89f99231cf35f7660a968b7","tid":2135370,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167d5c3cd65f8356faaf4601ff72bb1ea0f701ca","tid":2135370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"有D銀行去到12個月<br />\n<br />\n[url]ttps://<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/article/143997/理財/銀行-還息不還本-業主-月慳開支6成/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F143997%2F%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%2F%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-%E9%82%84%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%8D%E9%82%84%E6%9C%AC-%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB-%E6%9C%88%E6%85%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF6%E6%88%90%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2cc3a0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.edigest.hk/article/143997/理財/銀行-還息不還本-業主-月慳開支6成/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n15間銀行推「還息不還本」長達12個月 業主月慳近6成開支逾20,000元<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情未止，本港失業率又按年升至3.4%，為紓緩疫情對巿民影響，銀行推出臨時紓困措施，與客戶共同渡過難關。尤其在物業按揭方面，「還息不還本」措施可以讓業主暫時紓緩供款壓力。綜觀提供給個人客戶受惠的15間銀行，物業按揭「還息不還本」，一般最長介乎6至12個月。有專家指，以年前借貸400萬元為例，首年每月開支或可減少逾萬元；貸款額1,000萬元的借款人，每月供款減少逾26,000元。惟要注意，過了優惠期，有機會增加總供款開支。"}]}